    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《卡牌术士》是一款轻度肉鸽地牢探险游戏。深入怪物肆虐的深渊，以技能卡牌为武器。在层层下探的过程中斩灭敌人与首领，构筑牌组，释放强力组合技。每次冒险都是全新的胜利之路——掌握卡牌间的精妙配合，打造属于你的独特战术。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >警告：这是一个小型游戏。内容仅包括：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >35 张卡牌<br>12 种附魔<br>4 个Boss<br><br>(演示动图为英文界面，但游戏内支持简体中文。)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276950/extras/12e6abcfcdb1f2cc4c0822647b80e88b.poster.avif?t=1751398940\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276950/extras/12e6abcfcdb1f2cc4c0822647b80e88b.webm?t=1751398940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276950/extras/12e6abcfcdb1f2cc4c0822647b80e88b.mp4?t=1751398940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276950/extras/1b2fecaf8c623dfd095f62c37631f589.poster.avif?t=1751398940\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276950/extras/1b2fecaf8c623dfd095f62c37631f589.webm?t=1751398940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276950/extras/1b2fecaf8c623dfd095f62c37631f589.mp4?t=1751398940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276950/extras/5767bbdcfd94b890d7f3e2fb50c6c97c.poster.avif?t=1751398940\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276950/extras/5767bbdcfd94b890d7f3e2fb50c6c97c.webm?t=1751398940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=v